      "time": 9.7,
      "time_str": "00:09.700",
      "text": "请你不要再迷恋哥，哥只是一个传说",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 15.39,
      "time_str": "00:15.390",
      "text": "虽然我 舍不得 可是我 还是要说",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 20.6,
      "time_str": "00:20.600",
      "text": "你不要再迷恋我，我只是一个传说",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 26.45,
      "time_str": "00:26.450",
      "text": "我不曾寂寞，因为有你曾陪着我",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 31.39,
      "time_str": "00:31.390",
      "text": "When everybody says someone is a hero",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 34.3,
      "time_str": "00:34.300",
      "text": "No one really knows the truth about an idol",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 37.0,
      "time_str": "00:37.000",
      "text": "Whose inside is pretty lonely n' vulnerable",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 39.51,
      "time_str": "00:39.510",
      "text": "Wishing there'll be someone who do know",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 41.89,
      "time_str": "00:41.890",
      "text": "One time, he set himself a high goal",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 44.6,
      "time_str": "00:44.600",
      "text": "He wants to be there as a role model",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 47.03,
      "time_str": "00:47.030",
      "text": "Ever since then life becomes a live show",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 49.98,
      "time_str": "00:49.980",
      "text": "Real time show without any rehearsal",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 52.575,
      "time_str": "00:52.575",
      "text": "每一个传说 都会随时间褪色",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 57.146,
      "time_str": "00:57.146",
      "text": "每个强者都会有 背后的辛酸挫折",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 62.344,
      "time_str": "01:02.344",
      "text": "之所以活的洒脱 是因为懂得取舍",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 68.21,
      "time_str": "01:08.210",
      "text": "之所以淡漠 是把一切都看破",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
